Inspired by this post with instructions including how to set up your own vim settings in github and manage with Pathogen

http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/johnpoelstra

Create symlinks:
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
